<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>PLACESIGHT — Brand Handbook</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Serif+Display:ital@0;1&family=DM+Mono:wght@300;400;500&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --black: #0a0a09;
  --white: #f5f4f0;
  --warm: #e8e4db;
  --accent: #c8b89a;
  --dim: #6b6860;
  --border: rgba(200,184,154,0.2);
  --serif: 'DM Serif Display', Georgia, serif;
  --mono: 'DM Mono', monospace;
  --sans: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
}
* { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
body { background: var(--black); color: var(--white); font-family: var(--sans); font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.6; overflow-x: hidden; }

nav { position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100; padding: 18px 40px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; background: rgba(10,10,9,0.92); backdrop-filter: blur(12px); border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border); }
.nav-logo { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.15em; color: var(--accent); text-transform: uppercase; }
.nav-links { display: flex; gap: 28px; }
.nav-links a { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: var(--dim); text-decoration: none; text-transform: uppercase; transition: color 0.2s; }
.nav-links a:hover { color: var(--white); }

.hero { min-height: 100vh; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: flex-end; padding: 120px 40px 60px; position: relative; border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border); }
.hero-label { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.15em; color: var(--accent); text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 24px; }
.hero-title { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: clamp(48px, 8vw, 96px); line-height: 1.0; color: var(--white); max-width: 800px; margin-bottom: 40px; }
.hero-title em { font-style: italic; color: var(--accent); }
.hero-statement { max-width: 560px; font-size: 14px; color: var(--dim); line-height: 1.7; border-left: 1px solid var(--accent); padding-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 60px; }
.hero-meta { display: flex; gap: 40px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.hero-meta-item { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10px; color: var(--dim); letter-spacing: 0.08em; }
.hero-meta-item span { display: block; color: var(--white); font-size: 13px; margin-top: 4px; }
.hero-grid-bg { position: absolute; inset: 0; background-image: linear-gradient(var(--border) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, var(--border) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 80px 80px; pointer-events: none; opacity: 0.4; }

section { padding: 80px 40px; border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border); }
.section-label { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.12em; color: var(--accent); text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 40px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
.section-label::after { content: ''; flex: 1; height: 0.5px; background: var(--border); max-width: 200px; }
.section-title { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 48px); line-height: 1.15; color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 16px; }
.section-sub { font-size: 13px; color: var(--dim); max-width: 500px; margin-bottom: 40px; line-height: 1.7; }

.ps-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 13px; }
.ps-table th { padding: 10px 16px; font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--dim); border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border); text-align: left; background: rgba(200,184,154,0.04); }
.ps-table td { padding: 14px 16px; border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border); color: rgba(245,244,240,0.75); vertical-align: top; line-height: 1.6; }
.ps-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
.ps-table td:first-child { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.06em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent); width: 160px; }
.ps-table .group-row td { background: rgba(200,184,154,0.06); font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--dim); padding: 8px 16px; }
.table-wrap { border: 0.5px solid var(--border); border-radius: 4px; overflow: hidden; }

.tag { display: inline-block; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 2px; font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10px; margin: 2px 2px 0 0; }
.tag-pass { background: rgba(120,180,140,0.15); color: #78b48c; border: 0.5px solid rgba(120,180,140,0.3); }
.tag-fail { background: rgba(180,100,80,0.15); color: #c87860; border: 0.5px solid rgba(180,100,80,0.3); }
.tag-neutral { background: rgba(200,184,154,0.1); color: var(--accent); border: 0.5px solid var(--border); }

.filter-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1px; background: var(--border); border: 0.5px solid var(--border); border-radius: 4px; overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 40px; }
.filter-card { background: var(--black); padding: 28px; }
.filter-num { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 36px; color: var(--border); margin-bottom: 12px; line-height: 1; }
.filter-name { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 20px; color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 6px; }
.filter-q { font-size: 12px; color: var(--dim); font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.5; }
.filter-copy { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 11px; color: var(--accent); border-left: 1px solid var(--accent); padding-left: 12px; line-height: 1.5; margin-top: 12px; }

.copy-grid { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1px; background: var(--border); border: 0.5px solid var(--border); border-radius: 4px; overflow: hidden; }
.copy-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 100px 1fr 1fr; background: var(--black); }
.copy-type { padding: 16px; background: rgba(200,184,154,0.04); font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--dim); border-right: 0.5px solid var(--border); display: flex; align-items: center; }
.copy-bad { padding: 16px; font-size: 12px; color: rgba(200,100,80,0.7); border-right: 0.5px solid var(--border); line-height: 1.5; }
.copy-good { padding: 16px; font-size: 12px; color: rgba(120,180,140,0.9); line-height: 1.5; }
.copy-head-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 100px 1fr 1fr; background: rgba(200,184,154,0.06); border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border); }
.copy-head-cell { padding: 8px 16px; font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--dim); }
.copy-head-cell:nth-child(2) { border-left: 0.5px solid var(--border); border-right: 0.5px solid var(--border); color: rgba(200,100,80,0.6); }
.copy-head-cell:nth-child(3) { color: rgba(120,180,140,0.7); }

.pattern-wrap { margin-bottom: 40px; }
.week-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 80px repeat(7, 1fr); gap: 1px; margin-bottom: 1px; }
.week-cell { padding: 12px 10px; font-size: 11px; line-height: 1.4; min-height: 70px; }
.day-label { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--dim); display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 0 10px; }
.day-head { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--dim); padding: 8px 10px; text-align: center; background: rgba(200,184,154,0.04); border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border); }
.cell-single { background: rgba(120,180,140,0.08); border: 0.5px solid rgba(120,180,140,0.2); }
.cell-antho { background: rgba(200,184,154,0.1); border: 0.5px solid rgba(200,184,154,0.3); }
.cell-reel { background: rgba(100,140,200,0.08); border: 0.5px solid rgba(100,140,200,0.2); }
.cell-rest { background: transparent; border: 0.5px solid var(--border); }
.cell-type { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 8px; letter-spacing: 0.06em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 4px; }
.cell-single .cell-type { color: rgba(120,180,140,0.8); }
.cell-antho .cell-type { color: var(--accent); }
.cell-reel .cell-type { color: rgba(100,140,200,0.8); }
.cell-desc { font-size: 10px; color: rgba(245,244,240,0.5); }
.cell-rest .cell-desc { color: var(--dim); font-size: 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; height: 100%; opacity: 0.3; }

.universe-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1px; background: var(--border); border: 0.5px solid var(--border); border-radius: 4px; overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 24px; }
.universe-card { background: var(--black); padding: 24px; }
.uni-pct { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 40px; color: var(--border); line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 8px; }
.uni-title { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 18px; color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 4px; }
.uni-sub { font-size: 11px; color: var(--dim); margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.5; }
.uni-list { list-style: none; }
.uni-list li { font-size: 11px; color: rgba(245,244,240,0.5); padding: 4px 0; border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border); display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }
.uni-list li::before { content: '—'; color: var(--accent); font-size: 10px; flex-shrink: 0; }
.uni-list li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

.who-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 24px; }
.who-card { padding: 28px; border: 0.5px solid var(--border); border-radius: 4px; }
.who-card.is { border-color: rgba(120,180,140,0.3); }
.who-card.not { border-color: rgba(180,100,80,0.2); }
.who-title { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 16px; }
.who-card.is .who-title { color: rgba(120,180,140,0.8); }
.who-card.not .who-title { color: rgba(180,100,80,0.6); }
.who-item { font-size: 12px; padding: 6px 0; border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border); display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: flex-start; line-height: 1.4; }
.who-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.who-card.is .who-item { color: rgba(245,244,240,0.7); }
.who-card.not .who-item { color: rgba(245,244,240,0.4); }
.who-dot { font-size: 10px; margin-top: 1px; flex-shrink: 0; }
.who-card.is .who-dot { color: rgba(120,180,140,0.6); }
.who-card.not .who-dot { color: rgba(180,100,80,0.4); }

.statement { padding: 60px 40px; border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border); display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 80px; align-items: center; }
.statement-text { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: clamp(20px, 2.5vw, 28px); line-height: 1.4; color: var(--white); }
.statement-text em { font-style: italic; color: var(--accent); }
.statement-meta { font-size: 12px; color: var(--dim); line-height: 1.7; }
.statement-meta strong { color: var(--white); font-weight: 400; display: block; margin-bottom: 6px; margin-top: 16px; font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; }
.statement-meta strong:first-child { margin-top: 0; }

.tone-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr); gap: 1px; background: var(--border); border: 0.5px solid var(--border); border-radius: 4px; overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 40px; }
.tone-card { background: var(--black); padding: 24px 20px; }
.tone-word { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 18px; color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 8px; }
.tone-desc { font-size: 11px; color: var(--dim); line-height: 1.5; }

.legend { display: flex; gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.legend-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10px; color: var(--dim); letter-spacing: 0.06em; }
.legend-dot { width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 2px; }

.ig-note { background: rgba(200,184,154,0.05); border: 0.5px solid var(--border); border-radius: 4px; padding: 24px 28px; margin-top: 40px; }
.ig-note-title { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 12px; }
.ig-note-body { font-size: 12px; color: var(--dim); line-height: 1.7; }
.ig-note-body strong { color: var(--white); font-weight: 400; }

footer { padding: 40px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
.footer-logo { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.15em; color: var(--accent); text-transform: uppercase; }
.footer-note { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10px; color: var(--dim); letter-spacing: 0.06em; }

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  nav { padding: 16px 20px; } .nav-links { display: none; }
  section { padding: 60px 20px; } .hero { padding: 100px 20px 50px; }
  .filter-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .universe-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .tone-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; } .who-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .statement { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
  .week-row { grid-template-columns: 50px repeat(7, 1fr); } .week-cell { padding: 8px 6px; }
  .copy-row { grid-template-columns: 80px 1fr; } .copy-bad { display: none; }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <div class="nav-logo">Placesight — Brand Handbook</div>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a href="#identity">Identity</a>
    <a href="#filter">Filter</a>
    <a href="#universe">Universe</a>
    <a href="#tone">Tone</a>
    <a href="#copy">Copy</a>
    <a href="#calendar">Calendar</a>
    <a href="#audience">Audience</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-grid-bg"></div>
  <div class="hero-label">Brand Handbook — v1.0</div>
  <h1 class="hero-title">Places<br>in <em>Plain</em>sight.</h1>
  <p class="hero-statement">PLACESIGHT is a discovery platform and visual archive of curated spaces, contemporary culture, and lifestyle. Believing that stories and inspiration hide in plainsight, the platform exists for those who notice.</p>
  <div class="hero-meta">
    <div class="hero-meta-item">Platform<span>Instagram · Web</span></div>
    <div class="hero-meta-item">Region<span>Thailand → SEA</span></div>
    <div class="hero-meta-item">Audience<span>20–40</span></div>
    <div class="hero-meta-item">Language<span>EN overlay · TH/EN caption</span></div>
  </div>
</div>

<section id="identity">
  <div class="section-label">01 — Identity</div>
  <h2 class="section-title">What Placesight is.</h2>
  <p class="section-sub">Not a review account. Not a travel guide. A platform with a point of view.</p>
  <div class="table-wrap">
    <table class="ps-table">
      <tr class="group-row"><td colspan="2">Core</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Identity</td><td>Discovery platform and visual archive for place, culture, and lifestyle — curated for people 20–40 who want to experience things worth finding, before they're obvious.</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Worldview</td><td>There are spaces and things made with intention everywhere. Most people walk past them. Placesight finds them first — then tells you why they matter.</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Core question</td><td><em>"What's the story here — beyond the fact that it looks good?"</em></td></tr>
      <tr><td>Feeling</td><td>"I found this before everyone else did." — accessible enough to share with anyone, but curated enough to feel proud doing it.</td></tr>
      <tr class="group-row"><td colspan="2">Brand Statement</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Full</td><td>PLACESIGHT is a discovery platform and visual archive of curated spaces, contemporary culture, and lifestyle. Believing that stories and inspiration hide in plainsight, the platform exists for those who notice.</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Short</td><td>A discovery platform and visual archive. For those who notice.</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Keywords</td><td><span class="tag tag-neutral">Place</span><span class="tag tag-neutral">Culture</span><span class="tag tag-neutral">Lifestyle</span><span class="tag tag-neutral">Discovery</span><span class="tag tag-neutral">Archive</span></td></tr>
      <tr class="group-row"><td colspan="2">What Placesight is NOT</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Not</td><td>A review account · A tourist guide · A cafe-hopping checklist · A cultural journal · An architecture magazine · A sponsored post feed</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Reference</td><td>Sits between Hypebeast (confident, cultural authority) and Kinfolk (slow, human, specific) — with the accessibility of Korean travel IG done with more editorial filter.</td></tr>
    </table>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="filter">
  <div class="section-label">02 — The Filter</div>
  <h2 class="section-title">5 questions before<br>every post.</h2>
  <p class="section-sub">If a place can't answer at least 3 of these — it doesn't go up. No matter how beautiful it is.</p>
  <div class="filter-grid">
    <div class="filter-card">
      <div class="filter-num">01</div>
      <div class="filter-name">Contrast</div>
      <div class="filter-q">"Why does this exist here — of all places?"</div>
      <span class="tag tag-pass">unexpected location</span><span class="tag tag-pass">context mismatch</span><br><br>
      <span class="tag tag-fail">pretty but predictable</span>
      <div class="filter-copy">"Feels like Copenhagen. It's in Ratchathewi."</div>
    </div>
    <div class="filter-card">
      <div class="filter-num">02</div>
      <div class="filter-name">Intention</div>
      <div class="filter-q">"Did someone make a deliberate decision to create this?"</div>
      <span class="tag tag-pass">maker has a why</span><span class="tag tag-pass">nothing here is accidental</span><br><br>
      <span class="tag tag-fail">trend-following · no reason behind it</span>
      <div class="filter-copy">"The light comes from one direction. That was a choice."</div>
    </div>
    <div class="filter-card">
      <div class="filter-num">03</div>
      <div class="filter-name">Story</div>
      <div class="filter-q">"What would you tell a friend about this place?"</div>
      <span class="tag tag-pass">detail people don't know</span><span class="tag tag-pass">copy writes itself</span><br><br>
      <span class="tag tag-fail">can only say "it's nice"</span>
      <div class="filter-copy">"Open a year. Still no sign. That's intentional."</div>
    </div>
    <div class="filter-card">
      <div class="filter-num">04</div>
      <div class="filter-name">Feeling</div>
      <div class="filter-q">"What will people feel here that they can't feel anywhere else?"</div>
      <span class="tag tag-pass">specific emotion · stays with you</span><br><br>
      <span class="tag tag-fail">good · nice · comfortable — interchangeable</span>
      <div class="filter-copy">"People go in for 10 minutes and leave 2 hours later."</div>
    </div>
    <div class="filter-card" style="grid-column: span 2;">
      <div class="filter-num">05</div>
      <div class="filter-name">Timing</div>
      <div class="filter-q">"Is Placesight early enough — or does it have a new angle on something already known?"</div>
      <span class="tag tag-pass">not yet famous</span><span class="tag tag-pass">famous but this angle is new</span><span class="tag tag-pass">about to disappear</span><br><br>
      <span class="tag tag-fail">everyone has posted it · nothing new to say</span>
      <div class="filter-copy">"If Placesight posts it, it's not obvious yet. But it will be."</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="universe">
  <div class="section-label">03 — Content Universe</div>
  <h2 class="section-title">Place · Culture · Lifestyle.</h2>
  <p class="section-sub">Three pillars. One filter. Everything posted must pass the same 5 questions — regardless of category.</p>
  <div class="universe-grid">
    <div class="universe-card">
      <div class="uni-pct">70%</div>
      <div class="uni-title">Place</div>
      <div class="uni-sub">Spaces that have something to say beyond looking good.</div>
      <ul class="uni-list">
        <li>Cafe — design-led, not trend-led</li>
        <li>Hotel / Boutique stay</li>
        <li>Architecture / Interior</li>
        <li>Art space / Gallery</li>
        <li>Independent bookshop</li>
        <li>Community / Studio space</li>
        <li>Destination / Neighbourhood</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="universe-card">
      <div class="uni-pct">15%</div>
      <div class="uni-title">Culture</div>
      <div class="uni-sub">The people and scenes that make places what they are.</div>
      <ul class="uni-list">
        <li>Maker / Architect / Founder</li>
        <li>The person behind the place</li>
        <li>Scene that only happens here</li>
        <li>Community space + what it enables</li>
        <li>Visual archive / Detail shot</li>
        <li>In transit / Journey</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="universe-card">
      <div class="uni-pct">15%</div>
      <div class="uni-title">Lifestyle</div>
      <div class="uni-sub">Objects and things that tell you who someone is.</div>
      <ul class="uni-list">
        <li>Furniture / Material</li>
        <li>Perfume / Scent</li>
        <li>Ceramics / Craft object</li>
        <li>Publication / Zine</li>
        <li>Garment / Accessory</li>
        <li>Everyday tool with design intent</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="table-wrap">
    <table class="ps-table">
      <thead><tr><th>Series</th><th>Format</th><th>Copy hook</th><th>Job</th><th>Freq</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr class="group-row"><td colspan="5">Discovery</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Single Place</td><td>1 photo · feeling-first</td><td>Tension / Contrast / Insider</td><td>Archive + trust</td><td><span class="tag tag-neutral">3×/week</span></td></tr>
        <tr><td>5 Places to ___</td><td>Carousel — emotion hook cover</td><td>"5 places for people who need to disappear"</td><td>Reach + shares</td><td><span class="tag tag-neutral">1×/week</span></td></tr>
        <tr><td>Place to Place</td><td>Journey format</td><td>"3 hours for what — then you understand."</td><td>Humanise brand</td><td><span class="tag tag-neutral">2×/month</span></td></tr>
        <tr><td>Without Google Maps</td><td>Single — hint, no pin</td><td>"If you find it, you'll know why."</td><td>Community + DMs</td><td><span class="tag tag-neutral">2×/month</span></td></tr>
        <tr class="group-row"><td colspan="5">Culture</td></tr>
        <tr><td>The Maker</td><td>Profile — person behind place</td><td>"The owner didn't want it to be famous. It happened anyway."</td><td>Depth + authority</td><td><span class="tag tag-neutral">2×/month</span></td></tr>
        <tr><td>The Take</td><td>Pure graphic / opinion</td><td>Placesight's point of view — no place, just a statement</td><td>Brand voice</td><td><span class="tag tag-neutral">1×/month</span></td></tr>
