  <h2 class="section-title">A friend with better taste.<br><em>Not a critic.</em></h2>
  <p class="section-sub">Placesight sounds like someone who has been there, chose to tell you about it, and trusts you to make your own decision.</p>
  <div class="tone-grid">
    <div class="tone-card"><div class="tone-word">Confident</div><div class="tone-desc">Says something is worth finding without asking for agreement.</div></div>
    <div class="tone-card"><div class="tone-word">Specific</div><div class="tone-desc">Never "nice atmosphere." Always why.</div></div>
    <div class="tone-card"><div class="tone-word">Unhurried</div><div class="tone-desc">No urgency. No FOMO. No countdown.</div></div>
    <div class="tone-card"><div class="tone-word">Dry</div><div class="tone-desc">Lets the place speak. Doesn't oversell it.</div></div>
    <div class="tone-card"><div class="tone-word">Human</div><div class="tone-desc">Someone went there. Felt something. Chose to share it.</div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="table-wrap">
    <table class="ps-table">
      <thead><tr><th>Rule</th><th>Never</th><th>Always</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>Opening</td><td>สวยมาก · น่ารักมาก · must visit</td><td>A fact or feeling that makes you stop</td></tr>
