  <div class="ig-note">
    <div class="ig-note-title">IG Algorithm — what matters right now</div>
    <div class="ig-note-body">
      <strong>Under 10K followers:</strong> Reels get 1.5× more reach than static posts. One Reel minimum per week.<br><br>
      <strong>Carousel posts</strong> drive the most saves. Saves tell the algorithm this content is worth pushing further — prioritise carousel for Anthology posts.<br><br>
      <strong>First 3 seconds of every Reel</strong> determines amplification. Visual movement or strong opening frame — no logo animation, no slow fade-in. Drop viewers straight into the best moment.<br><br>
      <strong>Posting time:</strong> Tue and Thu evenings 7–9 PM Bangkok. Sunday midday for Anthology reach posts.<br><br>
      <strong>Tracking:</strong> Add UTM tags to link in bio from day one. Use Instagram Insights weekly to see which post type and which location drives the most saves and shares — that's the content to double down on.
    </div>
